@Auth.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001

### Health Check
GET {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/health

### Swagger OpenAPI
GET {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json

### Swagger UI
GET {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/swagger

### ===== AUTENTICAÇÃO =====

### Registrar novo usuário (Aluno)
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "senha": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "dataNascimento": "1995-05-15T00:00:00",
  "ehAdministrador": false
}

### Registrar novo usuário (Admin)
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Admin",
  "email": "admin@teste.com",
  "senha": "AdminSenh@123",
  "dataNascimento": "1990-03-20T00:00:00",
  "ehAdministrador": true
}

### Login com usuário comum
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "senha": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### Login com admin
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@teste.com",
  "senha": "AdminSenh@123"
}

### Login com usuário padrão do sistema
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@auth.api",
  "senha": "Teste@123"
}

### Renovar token (substitua o refreshToken pelo valor recebido no login)
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI"
}

### ===== TESTES DE VALIDAÇÃO =====

### Registro com dados inválidos
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "",
  "email": "email-invalido",
  "senha": "123",
  "dataNascimento": "1995-05-15T00:00:00",
  "ehAdministrador": false
}

### Login com credenciais inválidas
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@inexistente.com",
  "senha": "SenhaErrada123"
}

### Refresh token inválido
POST {{Auth.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "token_invalido_aqui"
}
